<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q30_v2" title="Q30_v2" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceC</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>
      Dos amigos, Matías y Elisa, compran una caja de 
      <m:math><m:mn>40</m:mn></m:math>
      empanadas a un precio total de $
      <m:math><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>.
      Matías aporta $
      <m:math><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>
      y Elisa aporta el resto. Luego venden cada empanada a $
      <m:math><m:mn>1000</m:mn></m:math>
      y deciden repartirse el dinero obtenido de forma proporcional a lo que aportó cada uno.
    </p>
    <p>
      Se proponen los siguientes montos que podría recibir Matías: $
      <m:math><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>, $
      <m:math><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>, $
      <m:math><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>
      y $
      <m:math><m:mn>35&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>.
      Si el reparto se hace en forma proporcional al aporte de cada uno, 
      ¿cuál de estos montos es coherente con ese criterio de reparto?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">$15 000<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El dinero total obtenido por la venta es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>40</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>1000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>40&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Matías aportó <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>/</m:mo><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> del costo total, por lo que debe recibir <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>40&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Por eso, $15 000 no es coherente con el reparto proporcional.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">$20 000<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El total recaudado al vender las empanadas es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>40</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>1000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>40&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Como Matías aportó <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>/</m:mo><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> del dinero inicial, su parte debe ser <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>40&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Entonces, $20 000 no satisface el criterio de proporcionalidad.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">$30 000<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! El total recaudado es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>40</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>1000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>40&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Matías aportó <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>/</m:mo><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> del total inicial, así que debe recibir <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>40&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Por lo tanto, $30 000 es coherente con un reparto proporcional a su aporte.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">$35 000<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Al vender las <m:math><m:mn>40</m:mn></m:math> empanadas a $<m:math><m:mn>1000</m:mn></m:math> cada una, obtienen <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>40</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>1000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>40&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Matías aportó <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>/</m:mo><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> del costo total, así que le corresponde <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>40&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Por eso, $35 000 no es coherente con ese criterio de reparto.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Calcular cuánto aporta Elisa</strong></p>
            <p>El precio total de la caja es $20 000 y Matías aporta $15 000. Entonces Elisa aporta el resto:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>5&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Así, Matías aporta $15 000 y Elisa aporta $5 000.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Determinar la proporción del aporte de Matías</strong></p>
            <p>La fracción del total que aportó Matías es:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>15</m:mn><m:mn>20</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Entonces, Matías debe recibir <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> del dinero total obtenido en la venta.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Calcular el dinero total obtenido al vender las empanadas</strong></p>
            <p>Se venden <m:math><m:mn>40</m:mn></m:math> empanadas a $<m:math><m:mn>1000</m:mn></m:math> cada una:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>40</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>1000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>40&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>El dinero total recaudado es $40 000.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Calcular cuánto le corresponde a Matías</strong></p>
            <p>Como a Matías le corresponde <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> de $40 000, calculamos:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>40&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Por lo tanto, Matías debe recibir $30 000.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 5: Comparar con las alternativas dadas</strong></p>
            <p>Los montos propuestos son $15 000, $20 000, $30 000 y $35 000.</p>
            <p>El único monto que coincide con el reparto proporcional calculado es $30 000.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es <strong>ChoiceC</strong>: $30 000.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>